"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-30-team-gb-bmx-legend-kye-whyte-eyes-olympic-glory-21323382\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Kye Whyte made history by winningTeam GB's first ever BMX medal at theOlympicsby scooping a silver at Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kye_Whyte\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kye Whyte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kye_Whyte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kye_Whyte\"}, {\"begin\": 38, \"end\": 40, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8453282597909393, \"rank\": 0.18296409775194725, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After watching his team mate Bethany Shriever take gold in the women's race moments later, the 24-year-old made headlines with a photograph showing him scoop up Shriever in his arms after her body cramped up at the finishing line.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bethany Shriever\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Shriever\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The South-East Londoner has since gone on to win numerous other medals, including taking silver in the 2022 UCI BMX Racing World Championships in Nantes.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCI_Mountain_Bike_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.99975055437036, \"rank\": 0.0002495078678322263, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCI_Mountain_Bike_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCI_Mountain_Bike_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 458, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 492, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\", \"score\": 0.9999615713071586, \"rank\": 3.843016969882067e-05, \"text\": \"Nantes\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Nantes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then in February of this year, Whyte won gold at the BMX Racing World Cup in Brisbane, beating Switzerland's Cedric Butti by less than two hundredths of a second.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\", \"score\": 0.9928315591282795, \"rank\": 0.005498254385121284, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane_Lions\"}, {\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7804767730450767, \"rank\": 0.280464892137302, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He now has his sights set on continuing his winning streak at theParisgames.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Below, we chatted to Whyte about what makes BMX such a stand-out sport and why, despite numerous injuries and setbacks, he always returns to it.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was watching on the television the 2008summerOlympics inChina.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was when BMX made its Olympic debut and I remember being so excited to watch it.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was sat watching Liam Phillips compete as part of Team GB and thinking that is exactly what I want to do.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Phillips\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liam Phillips\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Phillips\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Phillips\"}, {\"begin\": 1094, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999992422461361, \"rank\": 6.243059936920003e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was around eight years old at the time and that was my goal, to get to the Olympics no matter what.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BMX racing is such a unique sport.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1253, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.217683593656669e-13, \"text\": \"BMX racing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I absolutely love the speeds we can go up too and the fact it is super-fast which is really exhilarating.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is one of the most dangerous sports and that's what I love; the danger element pushes me on to go further.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And when I win a race it is all worth it.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not really find anything hard about it but you have to have the right mind set and concentration.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your goal is to race fast and always think about not falling off your bike at the same time.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I always have to be focussed.\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is good to start at a young age if you like BMX riding, but there are people who develop a passion for it later in life.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd really recommend getting involved in your local BMX club and there you can take part in training sessions and learn the basic skills.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1950, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, if you are good enough, you can start competing in club races locally, then regional ones.\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There are local clubs all around the country who can teach you everything you need to know.\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I got my first taste of racing at the Peckham BMX Club, where my dad was a coach.\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2264, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peckham\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7282900883381945e-24, \"text\": \"Peckham\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peckham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peckham\"}, {\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a local club, it is excellent and helped teach me so much.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know my victory at the Olympics has inspired the next generation of BMX riders at the club too.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2440, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9987945704560207, \"rank\": 0.0012068793744397768, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew from a very early age I was going to make it as I felt so confident on the bike.\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was around ten year's old and was winning races against boys who were four years older than me.\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I won lots of British junior titles and so I knew I was good at what I did.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9986459663736788, \"rank\": 0.0012604435892965248, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knowing you are good at what you do powers you on to success.\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It definitely has to be the numerous Injuries I have sustained from falling off the bike.\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had so many accidents and setbacks during my recovery.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have broken both my collarbones, shoulders, my wrist, fingers and the worst accident happened when I was 13 years old.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I fell off the bike badly, broke my jaw and had a bleed on my brain.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in an induced-coma for days and it was a very worrying time as I could have died.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3223, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not compete for a year after that accident.\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, as with every setback I just recuperate and then get back on the bike.\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love it too much.\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so excited to get to Paris as I feel as though this is going to be my first Olympics experience as Tokyo had all the Covid restrictions in place.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3403, \"end\": 3408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996830411, \"rank\": 3.1695815047451587e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3481, \"end\": 3486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.834818458710464, \"rank\": 0.19785327334694106, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time I will have my family watching on, my friends and the fans support means everything.\", \"from\": 3528, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You never know what's going to happen as BMX racing is a hard one to judge but I will definitely have my eye on winning and bringing home a medal.\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3664, \"end\": 3674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.217683593656669e-13, \"text\": \"BMX racing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX_racing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kye Whyte is a P&G Ambassador for the Olympic Games Paris 2024    ArrowMORE:Team GB star made huge sacrifice to make Olympic memory he will 'remember forever'  ArrowMORE:UFC champion slams 'disgusting' Paris 2024 opening ceremony and says Russia should host Olympics  ArrowMORE:Disgraced Olympic commentator slams  'massive over-reaction' to sexist comments that got him sacked  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 3771, \"to\": 4260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3771, \"end\": 3780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kye_Whyte\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kye Whyte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kye_Whyte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kye_Whyte\"}, {\"begin\": 3786, \"end\": 3789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Procter_&_Gamble\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"P&G\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Procter_&_Gamble\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Procter_&_Gamble\"}, {\"begin\": 3941, \"end\": 3944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9999846650696618, \"rank\": 1.533516561613865e-05, \"text\": \"UFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 3973, \"end\": 3983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.33695121464229e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 4010, \"end\": 4016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.8877427408625892, \"rank\": 0.095171526413043, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 4394, \"to\": 4566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4456, \"end\": 4462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"score\": 0.6784377202964147, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Punchy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punchy,_Somme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know which team you support.Close  This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": []}]}"